024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI'm%20in%20love%20with%20the%20peony%20shade%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20subtle%20pink%20that%20looks%20cozy%20and%20inviting%2C%20especially%20in%20warm%20lighting.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b84f26c-3907-4dbc-b1ec-2e4b6883ec07%5C%22%3EComfort%20and%20cooling%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECozy%20Earth's%20bamboo%20sheets%20might%20literally%20be%20the%20most%20comfortable%20sheets%20I've%20ever%20tried%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I'm%20a%20tricky%20customer.%20I'm%20a%20hot%20sleeper%2C%20so%20I%20prioritize%20cooling%20and%20breathability%20above%20all%20else.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20also%20love%20the%20silky%20softness%20that%20usually%20comes%20with%20warmer%20sheets%20like%20cotton%20sateen%20or%20flannel.%20It's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20find%20a%20set%20of%20sheets%20that%20do%20both%2C%20but%20somehow%2C%20Cozy%20Earth%20has%20done%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20of%20all%2C%20these%20sheets%20are%2C%20no%20exaggeration%2C%20the%20absolute%20softest%20sheets%20that%20I've%20ever%20used.%20Bamboo%20is%20known%20for%20its%20softness%2C%20but%20Cozy%20Earth's%20sheets%20go%20a%20step%20beyond%2C%20with%20an%20ultra-velvety%20feel.%20When%20I%20slip%20into%20bed%20between%20Cozy%20Earth's%20sheets%2C%20I%20feel%20the%20stress%20and%20worries%20of%20the%20day%20melt%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20my%20boyfriend%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20sensitive%20to%20certain%20textures%20and%20picky%20about%20his%20bedding%20%E2%80%94%20attests%20that%20these%20sheets%20are%20fantastic.%20Before%20I%20started%20testing%20bedding%2C%20we%20used%20a%20fleece%20blanket%20instead%20of%20a%20top%20sheet%2C%20since%20we%20liked%20the%20softness%20against%20our%20skin.%20My%20boyfriend%20has%20been%20resistant%20to%20the%20top%20sheet%20change%2C%20but%20the%20bamboo%20top%20sheet%20is%20so%20soft%20we%20don't%20even%20think%20about%20the%20fleece%20blanket%20anymore%20(although%20I%20still%20understand%20and%20respect%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fis-a-top-sheet-necessary%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewho%20prefer%20not%20to%20use%20a%20top%20sheet%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they're%20not%20just%20soft%3A%20they're%20breathable%20and%20cooling%2C%20too.%20I%20tested%20these%20sheets%20in%20the%20peak%20of%20summer%20when%20Indiana%20was%20going%20through%20its%20humid%20cornsweat%20season%2C%20and%20it's%20like%20a%20fiery%20swamp%20outside.%20Despite%20these%20conditions%2C%20I%20slept%20easily%20each%20night.%20Even%20when%20testing%20specific%20cooling%20sheets%2C%20there's%20always%20been%20at%20least%20one%20night%20that%20I%20wake%20up%20in%20a%20sweat%2C%20but%20I'm%20happy%20to%20report%20that%20I%20never%20experienced%20this%20with%20Cozy%20Earth's%20sheets%20on%20my%20bed.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20though%2C%20I%20was%20never%20%3Cem%3Etoo%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecold%20%E2%80%94%20I%20always%20felt%20perfectly%20comfortable%20with%20a%20regulated%20temperature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252de1c1f-fb14-4d72-afe3-2358a67bc07e%5C%22%3EA%20perfect%20fit%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECozy%20Earth's%20sheets%20also%20fit%20the%20bed%20well.%20I'm%20a%20restless%20sleeper%2C%20so%20I%20need%20a%20sheet%20that%20fits%20snugly%20on%20my%20mattress%20without%20slipping%20off%20at%20night.%20I'm%20impressed%20by%20Cozy%20Earth's%20bamboo%20sheets%20because%20they%20fit%20on%20my%20mattress%2C%20regardless%20of%20height.%20I've%20been%20testing%20mattress%20toppers%2C%20adding%20three%20to%20four%20inches%20to%20my%20already%20thick%20mattress%2C%20but%20these%20sheets%20can%20handle%20it%2C%20with%2020-inch%20deep%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e17468cc-a631-450b-b48b-0a60c05c4247%5C%22%3EMade%20to%20last%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20softness%2C%20where%20Cozy%20Earth%20sheets%20stand%20out%20is%20in%20their%20durability.%20I've%20washed%20this%20set%20four%20times%2C%20and%20despite%20a%20small%20loss%20of%20sheen%2C%20I've%20noticed%20no%20difference%20in%20the%20sheet's%20texture.%20There's%20no%20pilling%2C%20loose%20threads%2C%20or%20visible%20scratches.%20Plus%2C%20the%20sheets%20feel%20even%20softer%20after%20each%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20durability%20is%20especially%20impressive%2C%20given%20that%20my%20dog%20likes%20to%20nest%20with%20his%20claws%20before%20he%20goes%20to%20sleep.%20Other%20sheets%20I've%20tried%20have%20given%20way%20to%20his%20nails%2C%20either%20snagging%20or%20ripping%20completely%2C%20but%20Cozy%20Earth's%20bamboo%20set%20has%20stayed%20strong.%20I'm%20looking%20forward%20to%20continuing%20to%20wash%20and%20use%20this%20set%20to%20observe%20it%20for%20signs%20of%20wear%20and%20tear.%20They%20still%20look%20as%20good%20as%20new%20after%20months%2C%20and%20if%20my%20predictions%20are%20correct%2C%20they'll%20hold%20up%20to%20years%20of%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ae19d36-e50c-480d-a86a-d6860ce297e9%5C%22%3ECare%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cozy%20Earth%20bamboo%20sheets%20are%20simple%20to%20care%20for%20and%20follow%20standard%20wash%20instructions.%20I%20wash%20with%20detergent%20with%20cool%20or%20cold%20water%20on%20a%20gentle%20setting%2C%20then%20transfer%20them%20to%20the%20dryer%20to%20tumble%20dry%20on%20low.%20I%20recommend%20removing%20the%20sheets%20from%20the%20dryer%20right%20away%2C%20as%20they%20tend%20to%20wrinkle%20when%20left%20in%20the%20dryer%20for%20too%20long.%20Cozy%20Earth%20also%20suggests%20washing%20sheets%20separately%2C%20especially%20from%20towels%20to%20avoid%20lint.%20I%20was%20careful%20not%20to%20use%20fabric%20softeners%20or%20harsh%20chemicals%20like%20bleach%2C%20which%20can%20break%20down%20the%20bamboo%20fibers.%20For%20more%20tips%20on%20caring%20for%20bamboo%20sheets%2C%20I%20recommend%20checking%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-wash-sheets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20to%20wash%20sheets%20article.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c9e37e2-4400-4946-ac7e-28244ea34dd5%5C%22%3EValue%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECozy%20Earth%20bamboo%20sheets%20are%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20a%20queen-size%20set%20will%20cost%20%24297.%20They're%20extraordinarily%20comfortable%20and%20durable%2C%20but%20I%20think%20they're%20a%20tad%20overpriced%2C%20especially%20compared%20to%20competitors.%20Fortunately%2C%20Cozy%20Earth%20frequently%20runs%20promotions%20around%20holiday%20shopping%20events%20like%20Memorial%20Day%20or%20Black%20Friday%2C%20where%20I've%20noticed%20you%20can%20save%20as%20much%20as%2035%25%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECozy%20Earth%20offers%20a%20100-night%20trial%20and%20a%2010-year%20warranty.%20If%20you%20decide%20they%20aren't%20for%20you%20within%20100%20nights%2C%20you%20can%20return%20them%20for%20a%20full%20refund.%20The%20sheets%20are%20protected%20from%20%26quot%3Bpilling%2C%20abnormal%20rips%20and%20tears%2C%20and%20workmanship%20defects%26quot%3B%20within%2010%20years%20of%20the%20purchase%20date.%20If%20you%20use%20your%20warranty%2C%20you'll%20receive%20a%20replacement%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221c2bbb96-97c3-438a-b6e4-ff6239f196ac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20image%20of%20the%20cozy%20earth%20bamboo%20sheet%20set%20on%20a%20bed%20and%20set%20of%20pillows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6893ae8c194a2d49b8ae1d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThese%20sheets%20are%20incredibly%20soft%2C%20but%20they're%20prone%20to%20wrinkling%20and%20look%20sheer%20on%20the%20bed.%20Plus%2C%20they're%20pretty%20expensive.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20main%20drawback%3F%20These%20sheets%20are%20%3Cem%3Eexpensive.%20%3C%2Fem%3EAlmost%20%24300%20for%20a%20queen-size%20set%20is%20nothing%20to%20sneeze%20at.%20Bamboo%20sheets%20are%2C%20in%20general%2C%20more%20expensive%20than%20cotton%20sheets%2C%20but%20Cozy%20Earth's%20bamboo%20set%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20on%20the%20market.%20You're%20paying%20for%20quality%20and%20durability%2C%20so%20it's%20a%20worthwhile%20investment%2C%20but%20it's%20definitely%20not%20a%20small%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOtherwise%2C%20we've%20noticed%20that%20the%20sheets%20lose%20their%20sheen%20after%20washing%2C%20something%20that%20Cozy%20Earth%20notes%20is%20normal%20for%20bamboo%20sheets.%20The%20sheets%20are%20on%20the%20thinner%20side%2C%20which%20helps%20with%20their%20airiness%2C%20but%20light%20colors%20are%20see-through.%20I%20can%20see%20my%20mattress%20and%20pillow%20logos%20through%20the%20fitted%20sheet%20and%20pillowcase.%20If%20that%20will%20bother%20you%2C%20I'd%20opt%20for%20a%20darker%20color%20like%20navy%20or%20charcoal.%20Mattress%20and%20pillow%20protectors%20can%20also%20help%20for%20a%20seamless%2C%20logo-free%20look.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20you%20can%20see%20by%20the%20pictures%2C%20the%20sheets%20are%20also%20prone%20to%20wrinkling%2C%20even%20when%20cared%20for%20properly.%20It's%20difficult%20to%20get%20a%20crisp%2C%20clean%2C%20made%20bed%20look%20with%20the%20top%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229761ff82-4dd1-4c8a-a859-cbbec3c49375%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20overall%20pick%20in%20our%20best%20bamboo%20sheets%20guide%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D48d5753231876885e4ddcc3d2ddaa5c531a187a420aae53de98b3f442a3c20ee%26postID%3D6893a649ef1e672788f167de%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcozy-earth-bamboo-sheets-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.quince.com%252Fhome%252Fbamboo-sheets%5C%22%20ta