0scrap%E2%80%99s%20journey%20was%20documented%2C%20from%20pick-up%20to%20recycling%2C%20thus%20enabling%20transparency%20and%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20pivotal%20client%20success%20story%20was%20with%20Aditya%20Birla%20Fashion.%20Before%20partnering%20with%20Let%E2%80%99s%20Scrap%2C%20their%20scrap%20handling%20was%20plagued%20by%20pilferage%20and%20inefficiencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnuj%E2%80%99s%20platform%20swiftly%20turned%20their%20yearly%20scrap%20collection%20into%20a%20bi-monthly%20exercise%2C%20unearthing%20previously%20unseen%20profits%20and%20reducing%20losses.%20This%20transformation%20of%20a%20cumbersome%2C%20opaque%20process%20into%20a%20well-oiled%2C%20profitable%20one%20exemplified%20the%20core%20mission%20of%20Let%E2%80%99s%20Scrap.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20Scrap%20serves%20three%20main%20types%20of%20customers%3A%20corporate%20clients%2C%20small%20retail%20shops%2C%20and%20households.%20It%20provides%20a%20digital%20platform%20for%20clients%2C%20which%20can%20be%20accessed%20via%20their%20website%20or%20mobile%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorporate%20clients%2C%20such%20as%20e-commerce%20and%20FMCG%20companies%20with%20multiple%20store%20locations%2C%20use%20this%20platform%20to%20schedule%20scrap%20collection.%20Each%20store%20is%20onboarded%20onto%20the%20platform%20as%20a%20collection%20point%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20schedule%20pick-ups%20based%20on%20their%20scrap%20generation%20frequency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollection%20agents%20from%20Let%E2%80%99s%20Scrap%20use%20their%20app%20to%20take%20photos%20and%20record%20material%20details%20digitally%20during%20pick-up.%20A%20digital%20invoice%20is%20generated%2C%20and%20the%20collected%20scrap%20is%20transported%20to%20a%20Material%20Recovery%20Facility%20(MRF)%2C%20where%20the%20scrap%20is%20sorted%20into%20categories%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F443701%2Fhulladek-recycling-e-waste-managemen